{"tid":1417152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求置頂］超重要，大家入黎諗新口號","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T17:05:05.000Z","uid":167174,"like":10,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"da9713727c4c87d4787783bb52e8c6553a6f7634","tid":1417152,"uid":167174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"大家都應該feel到光復香港、時代革命依個口號係有佢既問題。<br />\n<br />\n如果有幸既話，我建議喺依個post 諗新口號，conclude後再開新post，將口號寫喺標題度，再大量做文宣。<br />\n<br />\n八粒字，要有同樣既號召力，我相信難唔到連燈仔。<br />\n<br />\n我先拋個磚：<br />\n<br />\n警黑亂港 公民抗命<br />\n<br />\n（其實我覺得12字都有得諗）"},{"pid":"a9f2078b708fcd7ad1b7d2ec56b4e7ec59616842","tid":1417152,"uid":167174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:06:08.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3ca4d955b094d836ac90bd88985c80a073d29d4b","tid":1417152,"uid":167174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"自推 x 2"},{"pid":"743b8b7b6cf1c828adf632b65e67f6f6fd4b70e9","tid":1417152,"uid":167174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:06:57.000Z","msg":"自推 x 3"},{"pid":"d9cf27fe25ec01b3946b30378070596929da675c","tid":1417152,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:07:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">請全世界入黎！！究竟我地係咪要港獨？目標要一致！！<br />\n</span><br />\n如果唔係爭取港獨，請立即澄清<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416445</a>"},{"pid":"1570d8b08581ce281fd6e5e86b0eb995bf4513a8","tid":1417152,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:07:21.000Z","msg":"根本個口號係中共宣傳比大家<br />\n傻仔先會跟住叫"},{"pid":"e10544a62088f96b2e3310a125982d57a2fe8775","tid":1417152,"uid":167174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:07:32.000Z","msg":"自推 x 4"},{"pid":"f5385b31014f1e200805616b92d54754b7c874d8","tid":1417152,"uid":289394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:07